1
04:04:37,918 --> 04:04:39,168
[SQUAWKING]

2
04:04:41,171 --> 04:04:43,048
The Eagles are coming.

3
04:05:30,426 --> 04:05:31,680
[COUGHING AND GASPING]

4
04:05:33,348 --> 04:05:34,140
Bilbo.

5
04:05:34,391 --> 04:05:36,351
Don't move. Don't move. Lie still.

6
04:05:38,019 --> 04:05:40,563
Oh. Mm. Mm.

7
04:05:40,939 --> 04:05:42,114
I'm glad you are here.

8
04:05:42,315 --> 04:05:43,858
- Shh, shh.
- Unh.

9
04:05:44,818 --> 04:05:46,611
I wish to part from you in friendship.

10
04:05:46,861 --> 04:05:49,851
No...
You are not going anywhere, Thorin.

11
04:05:50,073 --> 04:05:51,408
You're going to live.

12
04:05:51,866 --> 04:05:54,953
- I would take back
my words and my deeds at the Gate.

13
04:05:56,788 --> 04:05:59,207
You did what only a true friend would do.

14
04:06:00,667 --> 04:06:02,320
Forgive me.

15
04:06:04,462 --> 04:06:06,548
I was too blind to see it.

16
04:06:08,925 --> 04:06:10,468
I am so sorry...

17
04:06:11,845 --> 04:06:13,722
...that I have led you into such peril.

18
04:06:14,889 --> 04:06:17,642
No, I'm glad to have shared
in your perils, Thorin.

19
04:06:17,892 --> 04:06:19,185
Each and every one of them.

20
04:06:22,605 --> 04:06:25,567
It is far more than any Baggins deserves.

21
04:06:29,988 --> 04:06:31,238
Farewell...

22
04:06:32,115 --> 04:06:33,908
...Master Burglar.

23
04:06:35,243 --> 04:06:37,287
Go back to your books.

24
04:06:38,455 --> 04:06:40,457
And your armchair.

25
04:06:42,208 --> 04:06:44,127
Plant your trees.

26
04:06:44,794 --> 04:06:46,463
Watch them grow.

27
04:06:47,922 --> 04:06:49,215
[GROANS]

28
04:06:51,509 --> 04:06:53,261
If more people...

29
04:06:54,304 --> 04:06:55,930
...valued home...

30
04:06:56,181 --> 04:06:58,141
...above gold...

31
04:06:59,142 --> 04:07:02,729
...this world would be a merrier place.

32
04:07:04,856 --> 04:07:05,899
[GRUNTS]

33
04:07:06,399 --> 04:07:08,693
No. No, no, no. No.

34
04:07:08,943 --> 04:07:11,363
Thorin. Thorin, now don't you dare...

35
04:07:13,656 --> 04:07:14,783
Thorin.

36
04:07:20,747 --> 04:07:23,124
Thorin. Thorin, hold on.

37
04:07:23,375 --> 04:07:24,701
Hold on, please.

38
04:07:25,085 --> 04:07:26,420
The Eagles...

39
04:07:26,920 --> 04:07:29,130
The Eagles... The Eagles are here.

40
04:07:29,798 --> 04:07:30,965
Thorin?

41
04:07:34,177 --> 04:07:35,427
The Ea...

42
04:07:36,805 --> 04:07:38,807
[SOBBING]

